{
  "stem": "1033.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because that-- you know, as a Jewish boy in Europe, you, you, you, you didn't have a chance if you were circumcised.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the very first thing I, I felt-- I'm safe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's other kids who are circumcised, people like myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they're not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's just an aside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, I don't know to what extent I have answered your question in terms of relevance to what people thought about the war.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We tried to forget about the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There is something in, in human nature-- there is certainly something in my own nature-- and I would say it's a good aspect-- that it tries to look for the lark aspect, the, the fun, the bizarre, the, the joyous.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The macabre goes nowhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, and having survived what I had survived personally-- and I can really only speak of myself-- I knew that that kind of thinking is a dead end.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I often speculated and wondered about my own mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because I, I, I am 64 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I still feel ripped off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I didn't have someone who, as a child, who had me in her arms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it's-- it-- it's, it's kind of lurid for me to speak of this right now.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I thought that if my mom hadn't been so terrified-- if, if she-- a sense of humor is so wonderful.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I mean terror, I am sure-- Hitler did not invent terror.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Human existence had always entailed an undesirable or, or worse aspect.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And people have always had to make the best of where they were, who they were, and where they hoped to go.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, so I, I-- I looked for the-- if not for the positive, then, then for the humorous.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
